                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.quests",
                    "id": "e84c5278-c8be-4d3c-930f-07221418702d",
                    "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                    "propId": "477d726c-f141-48fb-9bf7-514b37b647f4",
                    "target": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "98765f44-ee05-47f0-9ae2-e6c742c22a9d",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "5",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d82b6e5c-378f-49e8-8581-0df9307f1928",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Good afternoon, everyone, and welcome to our <i>Magic for Mundanes</i> class. All of you have shown only a minor talent for magic, poor dears. ",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "41398dc0-b0e0-453a-9387-2e6368495d71",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "However, even a little magic can work wonders!",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1bb66262-e885-4639-a9c5-a5f65998f985",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "In this elective session, you will first learn the basic principles of Wizardry and Magic. We will put that knowledge to use for some simple, very useful spells.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "2dfb5e85-3151-42a4-9f24-da693a60589c",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Finally, we will construct some practical magic items for all you gallant adventurers to use on your dangerous excursions!",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "6051bb85-a2a7-4eaa-8b5d-139b88bafb4c",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "As soon as you have finished your tea and biscuits, we shall get started. In the meanwhile, are there any questions or comments you would like to make?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "ae25f9cc-b99e-4119-a237-d24af032030a",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "a3ed1afa-4cc4-4576-8510-fb5895f1430d",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "0418de57-25c6-4f61-9c71-1c64c3ed193c",
                            "text": "Say Something Charming",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "dc694d74-274e-4a17-b5b6-8d98bf56997c",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "25",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "63e61610-d71f-4a59-8929-d5ad4c35eb88",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "This sounds like the best class I've ever taken... I've always been fascinated by magic so I can't wait to learn how to cast spells. And the tea and cookies are a great way to start the lessons.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "a2266a3e-cf1b-4161-aa36-f5c4322c13b9",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2a7d9427-c8fd-4989-bf36-1c93d800dc13",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "That's very sweet of you to say, thank you. However, I don't want to get your hopes up too much. The spells you will learn are minor. Then again, the knowledge you will learn is invaluable.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "50ebcda4-7651-4382-8cf3-0538a1df4c68",
                            "text": "Ask Something Intelligent",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "0e8f9e6f-8ab0-40dc-8864-00187dc7fa43",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "25",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "74f034c1-94d4-4afa-9bc1-5c499c24b2e7",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "b8f03736-f0f2-428a-b9ce-596c094f09a6",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "1",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0f5ae813-abbe-4a6b-b7f2-4a65a0c85a28",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "When you talk about casting spells, does this mean we get a magic wand to wave around?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e15f3269-96d2-49ad-96a2-29f0af7c1561",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Wave a Wand? Piffle. What a silly way to cast a spell! A true Wizard uses a proper staff to store her mojo and her spells.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "714c2675-2591-4a04-b889-0b3ccd29d97c",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Of course, you are not Wizards nor will you need a glorified stick with which to wield your magic. All you will need is your Will and your Wit.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "b070e308-9136-4456-a1a6-f242a5eff0a8",
                            "text": "Make a Snarky Comment",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "31fcf55d-669d-4458-9bbe-329bc2892ecf",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "25",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "bafc1fa8-e567-48ea-b18e-f18ac72c6109",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "1",
                                                "change": "0",
                                                "notify": false
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "60c26b99-6b48-4b9a-baf1-61394e40facf",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "So after the milk and cookies will you read us a story about cute little fairies?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a509263d-9202-491e-af1b-2e18491cc761",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I'll have you know that is good, rich cream for your tea, not mere milk. Nor do the Faerie folk consider themselves to be cute or little... You are undoubtedly thinking of Pixies.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8ac4bffe-f3a6-4e4d-a39b-1259abb811fe",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "We will focus this class on your personal magic rather than magical creatures. If you desire to learn more about the Fae or about Pixies, I suggest you research the subject in the library.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "42f9881f-449d-45eb-91cb-c48b295d707b",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Libraries, after all, are truly magical places for learning.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "53b5b070-81e8-4ae4-997e-1fb2e1453fe1",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0d039f44-3f7f-460b-99bb-55bbbafa7e47",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Very well, we shall get started with our introduction to practical magic for mundanes like you who manifest only minor magical proclivities...",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "34874534-ffe1-4a0b-83b7-d25826418871",
                    "name": "First Magic Class",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "Milk and cookies and comfy chairs... the perfect place to nap in the afternoon. This is a great class."
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
